data.title: St. John Fisher University, Rochester, NY
data.text:
Let’s Get Together

We are excited to welcome all St. John Fisher University alumni back to campus for Alumni Weekend, Friday, Sept. 20 through Sunday, Sept. 22. Register today.

This Fall...

...is the perfect time to see how impactful you can be at Fisher. Join us for an upcoming Fall Open House on October 12 or November 23. Register today!

Looking Ahead to Welcome Weekend

#Fisher2028, we look forward to seeing the newest flock of Cardinals for Orientation during Welcome Weekend. View Welcome Weekend details.

Language study is a powerful complement to any career. Focus on proficiency in one language, or double your linguistic prowess by studying two languages through this program.

Collaborative research, outstanding faculty, and the ability to tailor the curriculum to your interests are just some of the reasons to choose Fisher’s political science program.

“ I believe I have gotten great value out of my education at Fisher. The impact of great professors who are focused on the quality of your education paired with small classes is incredibly important. ”

“ Studying at Fisher will undoubtedly increase your academic and career opportunities. ”

“ I think what sets Fisher apart from other schools is the community and that professors are dedicated to you. ”

“ All of the hands-on experience I gained at Fisher helped me land an amazing job. The faculty are amazing people who love what they do and work hard to help students become successful graduates. ”

“ My Fisher education put me in the driver’s seat of my professional career. The opportunities for personal growth have been unmatched, and the tools and skills I have learned will stay with me for the rest of my life. ”
